    "body": "Here is an example to illustrate the problem. Once you click on the drop down you cannot select an option using the mouse. The only way to select an option is to use arrow keys and the enter key.\n\n``` html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n    <head>\n        <title>test</title>\n    </head>\n    <body>\n        <select>\n            <option value=\"test1\">Test #1</option>\n            <option value=\"test2\">Test #2</option>\n        </select>\n    </body>\n</html>\n```\n"
